  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下页面发布的完整生命周期。核心场景是零售客户忠诚度系统里的内容管理，从草稿到正式发布要分几个阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Page Publish Lifecycle",
        "Drafting",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以起点是草稿阶段。这个阶段创建页面时，published_at 应该是空值对吧？需要特别标注这是零售客户忠诚度相关的页面类型。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create page",
        "published_at is nil",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，草稿阶段还要能通过 content_page_blocks 添加内容区块。然后进入调度阶段，可以设置发布时间，这时候状态变成 scheduled。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Add content blocks",
        "content_page_blocks",
        "Scheduling",
        "Set published_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "调度阶段我想到一个细节：修改隐私设置、布局或 slug 时，缓存键要包含 updated_at。这个需要体现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Update privacy/layout/slug",
        "cached keys",
        "updated_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "需要，这是缓存失效的关键逻辑。最后是已发布阶段，判断标准是 published_at 小于等于当前时间。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Published",
        "published_at <= now"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "发布后的可见性逻辑我理一下：隐私设置为公开，或者用户有授权才能看到。这里用 policy allows 来表达可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visible if policy allows",
        "privacy public",
        "authorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍微调整一下，应该是「隐私公开」或「已授权」两种条件满足其一即可，不是同时满足。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "privacy public or authorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，三个阶段都齐了：草稿阶段包含创建页面和添加内容区块，调度阶段处理发布时间和元数据更新，已发布阶段处理可见性判断。我按这个结构画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
